@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Listar todas as tarefas
GET {{baseUrl}}/todos/

### Buscar tarefa por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/todos/1/

### Criar tarefa
POST {{baseUrl}}/todos/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user": 1,
  "title": "Estudar REST APIs",
  "completed": false
}

### Atualizar tarefa (completo)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/todos/1/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user": 1,
  "title": "Tarefa atualizada",
  "completed": true
}

### Marcar como concluída (parcial)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/todos/1/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "completed": true
}

### Deletar tarefa
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/todos/1/
